<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 18:14:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着电动汽车需求放缓，行业痛苦加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/industry-pain-abounds-electric-car-demand-hits-slowdown-2024-01-30/</link><description>尽管汽车制造商对电动汽车的未来需求下了很大的赌注，但近期的全球经济放缓正在带来痛苦。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 15:43:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/industry-pain-abounds-electric-car-demand-hits-slowdown-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>博尔顿在新回忆录介绍中称特朗普“不适合”担任总统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bolton-excoriates-trump-fresh-introduction-his-memoir-2024-01-30/</link><description>美国前国家安全顾问约翰·博尔顿在周二发布的新版回忆录中痛斥前总统唐纳德·特朗普是一个完全自私的人，他会惩罚私人敌人并安抚对手俄罗斯和中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 14:07:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bolton-excoriates-trump-fresh-introduction-his-memoir-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>IMF称全球“软着陆”在望，上调2024年增长前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-says-global-soft-landing-sight-raises-2024-economic-growth-outlook-2024-01-30/</link><description>国际货币基金组织上调了美国和中国的前景展望。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:08:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-says-global-soft-landing-sight-raises-2024-economic-growth-outlook-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织上调亚洲增长预测，警告中国风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imf-revises-up-asias-growth-forecast-warns-china-risk-2024-01-30/</link><description>国际货币基金组织 (IMF) 周二预计亚洲新兴经济体今年将增长 5.2%，较 2023 年有所放缓，但因中国经济增长强于预期而上调了三个月前的预测。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imf-revises-up-asias-growth-forecast-warns-china-risk-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>中美芬太尼合作北京期待“正能量”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-cooperate-fentanyl-beijing-hopes-positive-energy-2024-01-30/</link><description>周二，美国和中国成立了联合禁毒工作组，这是自 2019 年底以来两个超级大国双边关系恶化之前首次公开合作应对芬太尼泛滥。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:08:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-cooperate-fentanyl-beijing-hopes-positive-energy-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>台湾空军展示潜猎预警能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-air-force-shows-off-its-sub-hunting-early-warning-prowess-2024-01-30/</link><description>周二，台湾空军展示了全副武装的潜艇猎手以及预警和控制飞机，展示了它如何监视中国声称拥有主权的岛屿周围的天空和水域。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:47:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-air-force-shows-off-its-sub-hunting-early-warning-prowess-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商宁德时代预计2023年盈利增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-battery-giant-catl-expects-2023-earnings-jump-by-up-48-2024-01-30/</link><description>中国电动汽车 (EV) 电池巨头宁德时代 (CATL) 周二预计 2023 年净利润增长高达 48.1%，由于需求放缓和激烈竞争，该公司的增长大幅低于上年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-battery-giant-catl-expects-2023-earnings-jump-by-up-48-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：退款燃料、大型股更新、中国陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-30/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>德国将批准欧盟计划中的人工智能法案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/germany-will-approve-eus-planned-ai-act-sources-2024-01-30/</link><description>在负责数字问题的部长表示已经达成妥协后，德国将批准欧盟开创性的人工智能法案。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 10:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/germany-will-approve-eus-planned-ai-act-sources-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>印度4-12月钢铁进口量创五年新高 需求猛增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-december-steel-imports-hit-five-year-high-demand-soars-2024-01-30/</link><description>路透社周二看到的临时政府数据显示，截至3月底的本财年前9个月，印度钢铁进口量触及五年来新高，使该国成为成品钢材净进口国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:51:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-december-steel-imports-hit-five-year-high-demand-soars-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>恒大清算凸显投资者对中国债务的绝望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-liquidation-highlights-investor-despair-china-debts-2024-01-30/</link><description>中国负债最重的开发商的清算令开始了债权人漫长的程序，这可能会暴露出中国房地产低迷的严重程度，并导致建筑商被排除在全球债务市场之外，因为投资者回避风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:31:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/evergrande-liquidation-highlights-investor-despair-china-debts-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>红海危机和亚洲农历新年来临之际空运价格上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/air-freight-rates-rise-amid-red-sea-crisis-run-up-asias-lunar-new-year-2024-01-30/</link><description>在亚洲农历新年到来之前，全球空运价格出现七周以来的首次攀升，红海航运遭受的袭击促使企业寻求更昂贵的航空货运舱位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:07:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/air-freight-rates-rise-amid-red-sea-crisis-run-up-asias-lunar-new-year-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>印度限制措施推动巴基斯坦大米出口创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-curbs-propel-pakistans-rice-exports-towards-record-high-2024-01-30/</link><description>巴基斯坦的大米出口量可能会在截至 6 月份的一年中跃升至历史新高，因为其竞争对手印度决定限制本国的出货量，迫使买家从伊斯兰堡购买更多大米，而伊斯兰堡以近 16 年来的最高价格提供谷物。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 08:18:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indian-curbs-propel-pakistans-rice-exports-towards-record-high-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>恒大的命运取决于中国当局的承认</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/evergrandes-fate-hinges-recognition-china-authorities-2024-01-30/</link><description>恒大的任何清算都取决于中国当局是否承认香港法院的裁决，这一裁决也可能影响香港作为全球金融中心的地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 07:53:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/evergrandes-fate-hinges-recognition-china-authorities-2024-01-30/</guid></item><item><title>由于需求放缓，中国豆油、豆粕期货跌至六个月低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-soyoil-meal-futures-tumble-over-six-month-low-slowing-demand-2024-01-30/</link><description>周二，中国大连商品交易所豆油价格连续第三个交易日下跌，豆粕价格也因南美供应增长而需求放缓而下跌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 07:36:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-soyoil-meal-futures-tumble-over-six-month-low-slowing-demand-2024-01-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>